text: Nicolas Wildhaber (8 December 1929 – 26 September 2020) was a Swiss swimmer. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born in Zürich, Switzerland. Wildhaber died on 26 September 2020, aged 90. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Swiss swimmers Category:Olympians for Switzerland Category:Sportspeople from Zürich
